psychological_arc.arc_description: Started trusting but learned caution through betrayal

story_summary: agent_003 participated in 20 social interactions. They tried cooperating 10.0% of the time, but were betrayed 2 times. These experiences made them more loss-averse (sensitivity: 1.59). Their trust in others diminished to 0.00.
key_insights: Experienced 2 betrayals but kept trying to cooperate
Developed increased sensitivity to losses through experience
